  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Ability Score Increase.</strong> Your Intelligence score increases by 1</p>\n<p><strong>Warder's Intuition.</strong> Whenever you make an Intelligence <strong>(Investigation)</strong> check or an Ability Check involving @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-items.HWphIyqLmXJ56fRh]{Thieves' Tools}, you can roll a d4 and add the number rolled to the total ability check.</p>\n<p><strong>Wards and Seals.</strong> You can cast the @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.T6nNBhzyjOKZ0ueS]{Alarm} and @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.ZttvQx25TMC1Unxx]{Mage Armor} spells with this trait. Starting at 3rd level, you can also cast the @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.L6kpNwPGuT0Viiip]{Arcane Lock} spell with it. Once you cast either spell with this trait, you can't cast that spell again until you finish a <strong>Long Rest</strong>. Intelligence is your Spellcasting Ability for these spells, and you don't require material components when you cast them with this trait.</p>\n<p><strong>Spells of the Mark.</strong> If you have the Spellcasting or Pact Magic class feature, the spells on the Mark of Warding Spells table are added to the spell list of your Spellcasting class.</p>\n<p><strong>Mark of Warding Spells</strong></p>\n<table style=\"width:100%;height:323px\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"width:22.4373%;height:17px\"><strong>Spell Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:77.5627%;height:17px\"><strong>Spells</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:68px\">\n<td style=\"width:22.4373%;height:68px\">1st</td>\n<td style=\"width:77.5627%;height:68px\">@Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.T6nNBhzyjOKZ0ueS]{Alarm}, @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.g2B1luNF1dvQGWgA]{Armor of Agathys}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:68px\">\n<td style=\"width:22.4373%;height:68px\">2nd</td>\n<td style=\"width:77.5627%;height:68px\">@Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.L6kpNwPGuT0Viiip]{Arcane Lock}, @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.nsoDykkZYdD4AiSr]{Knock}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:51px\">\n<td style=\"width:22.4373%;height:51px\">3rd</td>\n<td style=\"width:77.5627%;height:51px\">@Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.kxzbQbqn423b53oz]{Glyph of Warding}, @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.8ridDHmAG0aBsugg]{Magic Circle}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:85px\">\n<td style=\"width:22.4373%;height:85px\">4th</td>\n<td style=\"width:77.5627%;height:85px\">@Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.gtx27BxxdA4bkcTM]{Leomund's Secret Chest}, @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.XWSubhualg7jVUGJ]{Mordenkainen's Faithful Hound}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:22.4373%;height:34px\">5th</td>\n<td style=\"width:77.5627%;height:34px\">@Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.iusFRYv0kuzXVDmg]{Antilife Shell}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
